{"tid":1386032,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(全民戴口罩) 一星期兩星期一個月","createTime":"2019-07-30T08:35:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T08:35:18.000Z","uid":282615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f3614ee10b6722b4fa8e42d3171665be3af1fe9f","tid":1386032,"uid":282615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T08:35:18.000Z","msg":"戴口罩都唔得？黑警強行搶走口罩<br />\n以後， <strong><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">黑警想視覺性騷擾女性咪好大鑊？</span></strong></strong><br />\n 女巿民拒絕响街上除衫，黑警係咪可強行脫去？<br />\n<br />\n不如發起全民戴口罩一星期、兩星期、一個月，黑警咁鍾意搶口罩，由佢地搶個夠，煩死佢地！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ktyTYo7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FktyTYo7.png&h=a9dcb240&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1385967\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1385967</a><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.facebook.com/groups/12786375244?view=permalink&amp;id=10162227156205245\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2F12786375244%3Fview%3Dpermalink%26id%3D10162227156205245&d=R3EG5gZ7WKeJnJLyvNLCuQ%2BnBs0jvEEXkL0KxwFTSeM%3D&h=916fadf2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://m.facebook.com/groups/12786375244?view=permalink&amp;id=10162227156205245</a>"}]}